title: Small Hydroelectric Engineering Practice
description:
English | 2014 | ISBN: 1138000981 | ISBN-13: 9781138000988 | 254 pages | PDF | 53,1 MB

Small Hydroelectric Engineering Practice is a comprehensive reference book covering all aspects of identifying, building, and operating hydroelectric schemes between 500 kW and 50 MW. 

In this range of outputs there are many options for all aspects of the scheme and it is very important that the best options are chosen.
